claim.claim-text:
1. A transaction terminal apparatus for executing settlement processing that requires a customer's signature with using a transaction medium that stores information for settlement, comprising: 
an acquisition unit for acquiring said information from said transaction medium; 
a control unit for proceeding with said settlement processing based on acquired said information and for requesting a signature from said customer at a prescribed stage in said settlement processing; 
an entering unit for entering a signature; and 
a display unit for displaying the signature entered from said entering unit.
